data.description: SELLERS ARE OFFERING $10,000 IN CLOSING COSTS OR TO BUY DOWN RATE!!!  Welcome to your dream home! This beautifully crafted residence offers a perfect blend of modern comforts and suburban serenity, nestled in a peaceful neighborhood. This home provides a wonderful backdrop for creating cherished memories with your loved ones.       As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living room, perfect for hosting gatherings or cozy family evenings. The open floor plan flows seamlessly from the living room to the dining area, creating an ideal space for entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight with its modern appliances, tons of counter space, and a breakfast bar! Whether you're preparing a quick meal or indulging in culinary adventures, this kitchen has you covered.       The generous master suite is a haven of relaxation, featuring a large sun-room, walk-in closet, and an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower; this retreat is perfect for unwinding after a long day. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests and each room is filled with natural light to offer a comfortable atmosphere. Awaiting the new owner is also a private office downstairs for anyone who works from home or could function as a 4th bedroom.       Step outside to discover the sprawling backyard oasis. This private space is ideal for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the Texas sunshine. Imagine barbecues, picnics, and gatherings with friends and family in this beautiful setting.       This home is conveniently located on the west side of San Antonio, offering easy access to University of Texas Health Science Center, Lackland AFB, major highways, employers, schools, shopping centers, and dining options. You'll have all the essentials at your fingertips while enjoying the peace and quiet of a suburban neighborhood. This home is move-in ready and designed for modern living. Explore nearby attractions like Government Canyon State Natural Area, SeaWorld San Antonio, and various parks, providing endless opportunities for outdoor adventures.        Don't miss your chance to make this charming house your new home. Schedule your showing today to experience the tranquility and comfort this property has to offer. Your Texas dream awaits!
